     <h3> <img class="ico" src="http://www.fyygcw.com/ygcw/view/skin/index/ico/ico014.gif" /><span><em>您现在的位置：<a href="http://www.fyygcw.com/cun/index/pid-01010322008.html">首页</a>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.fyygcw.com/cun/lanmu/pid-01010322008/id-8.html">组织机构</a></em></span> </h3> 
